		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />64x64 sprites are used in Chono Trigger during the time travel effect. They are used to &quot;simulate&quot; a BG which is transparent over the mode 7 BG.<br /><br />Final Fight 1 uses 8x8 and 16x16 sprites, while 2 and 3 uses 16x16 and 32x32 (during gameplay at least, I don't know if they use 64x64 elsewhere).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
