	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm sorry to necrobump this one, but I was aking myself :<br /><br />Which SNES games uses higher resolution than 256x240 ?<br /><br />I already know about Romanging SaGa3, Secret of Mana, Seiken Densetsu 3 and Rudra no Hiho who use a horizontal resolution of 512 for some of their parts (menus, and text boxes in the latter 2).<br /><br />However I don't know if any other games uses a horizontal resolution of 512, and if any game uses interlacing to get a pseudo-vertical resolution of 480.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


